<para id="element-35">
This vector equation can be equivalently written into three scalar component equations. For one dimensional case, however, we drop the vector notation altogether as in the case of linear momentum :
</para>
<para id="element-36">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
